            <title>格力官方旗舰店：纯铜电机落地扇 120 元政府补贴破冰新低</title>
            <link>https://lapin.ithome.com/html/digi/950060.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://lapin.ithome.com/html/digi/950060.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Wed, 13 May 2026 14:02:39 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
